        {
            "id": 6368988,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 萬豪國際(MAR-US)大跌5.01%，報316.35美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>萬豪國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MAR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MAR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MAR-US</a>)截至台北時間06日22:54股價下跌16.69美元，報316.35美元，跌幅5.01%，成交量199,339（股），盤中最高價326.73美元、最低價316.35美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.93%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1.71%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.4%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.75%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>萬豪國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MAR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MAR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MAR-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-4.17%</li> <li>近 1 月：+2.91%</li> <li>近 3 月：+14.82%</li> <li>近 6 月：+26.91%</li> <li>今年以來：+8.28%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6368988",
